    "title": "API Gateway 503s after TLS cert rotation",
    "severity": "P1",
    "summary": "The scheduled TLS cert rotation deployment deploy-tls-renew-v2 on the gateway service used a staging CA root that was accidentally included in the production bundle. All downstream services (orders, inventory) rejected the untrusted cert, causing 503s. The rollback deploy deploy-tls-rollback restored the previous cert chain at 11:12.\n",
    "affected_services": [
      "gateway",
      "orders",
      "inventory"
    ]
  },
